Scaling â†’ Java app scaled with HPA in Kubernetes.

Performance Issues â†’ high GC pauses â†’ fix via G1 GC + tuning.

Zero-Downtime Deployment â†’ rolling updates in Kubernetes with readiness probes.

âœ… Shows you can run Java apps in production at scale.

